{"tid":1058620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"崩牙駒入境菲律賓 被國際刑警拘捕","createTime":"2019-03-12T16:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T17:20:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6380d5de5fcf9ac0f03771346871fb16548b9218","tid":1058620,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"有菲律賓傳媒報道指，外號「崩牙駒」的澳門居民尹國駒入境當地時，在機場被國際刑警拘捕，澳門保安司表示，暫時未收到任何有關通報。<br />\n<br />\n根據菲律賓商報網頁消息，尹國駒昨日傍晚抵達馬尼拉亞基諾國際機場時，被當地的國際刑警逮捕，目前正拘留在當地移民局，但消息無透露尹國駒被拘捕原因，澳門保安司表示，根據法例，當局不能披露任何人士的出入境記錄。<br />\n<br />\n尹國駒在澳門回歸前，因涉及司警司司長白德安座駕爆炸案及多宗黑社會毆鬥、槍擊以及恐嚇案被捕，最後被法院判監15年，到2012年12月出獄。"},{"pid":"15f185d8ffbcde35762ff530f20e329e910392cd","tid":1058620,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"點解咁傻去菲律賓？"},{"pid":"46c9bda573cab784233946912f001afe6f0ea34e","tid":1058620,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"洗米華走定佬, 一家大細著硬草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf450acb2e25df7dbed9d8327b11704a68e724e7","tid":1058620,"uid":33077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46c9bda573cab784233946912f001afe6f0ea34e","tid":1058620,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"洗米華走定佬, 一家大細著硬草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"佢有錢過崩牙好多 應該無事"},{"pid":"fe3c5ab2d59696ef146dbe3761a497209033b81c","tid":1058620,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"痴線 比國際刑警拉 今次真係收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbbbf15ebcc6553d7f2406244fe2455884569cd","tid":1058620,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde790fa6bf7af8eb9fdf0244cc9a